# Nesting rules for conditional scopes:
#   - Max nesting depth is 2.
#   - 'docs' and 'upstream' scopes may contain nested conditionals.
#   - 'upstream' scopes may be nested inside any conditional.
#   - All other nesting is disallowed.
#

